{
  "page": "Lord of Stonehelm",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #DEDEE2; text-align:center;\">Lord of Stonehelm</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Office</th><td>\nRuler of <a href=\"/index.php/Stonehelm\" title=\"Stonehelm\">Stonehelm</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Region</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">Stormlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Current Holder</th><td>\nLord <a href=\"/index.php/Gulian_Swann\" title=\"Gulian Swann\">Gulian Swann</a> (or <a href=\"/index.php/Clifford_Swann\" title=\"Clifford Swann\">Clifford Swann</a>)</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Heir</th><td>\nSer <a href=\"/index.php/Donnel_Swann\" title=\"Donnel Swann\">Donnel Swann</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Lord of Stonehelm</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_a_son_for_a_son.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_a_son_for_a_son.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> is a title held by the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Swann\" title=\"House Swann\">House Swann</a>, the ruler of <a href=\"/index.php/Stonehelm\" title=\"Stonehelm\">Stonehelm</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">stormlands</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Known_Lords_of_Stonehelm\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Known Lords of Stonehelm</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_Stonehelm&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>When <a href=\"/index.php/Johanna_Swann\" title=\"Johanna Swann\">Johanna Swann</a> was captured by <a href=\"/index.php/Lysene\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lysene\">Lysene</a> captains of the <a href=\"/index.php/Triarchy\" title=\"Triarchy\">Triarchy</a>, her niggardly uncle, the Lord of <a href=\"/index.php/Stonehelm\" title=\"Stonehelm\">Stonehelm</a>, refused to pay her ransom.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Gawen_Swann\" title=\"Gawen Swann\">Gawen Swann</a> competed in the <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney_at_Ashford_Meadow\" title=\"Tourney at Ashford Meadow\">tourney at Ashford Meadow</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/209_AC\" title=\"209 AC\">209&#160;AC</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Before becoming a lord, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Manfred_Swann\" title=\"Manfred Swann\">Manfred Swann</a> had a young <a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Barristan Selmy</a> as his squire.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_Stonehelm&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_Stonehelm&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Gulian_Swann\" title=\"Gulian Swann\">Gulian Swann</a> agrees to meet Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Davos_Seaworth\" title=\"Davos Seaworth\">Davos Seaworth</a> but refuses to join the cause of <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racokprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racokprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup> During the <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">War of the Five Kings</a>, Gulian remains in his castle pleading <a href=\"/index.php/Illness\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Illness\">illness</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_Stonehelm&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Clifford_Swann\" title=\"Clifford Swann\">Clifford Swann</a> is listed as Lord of Stonehelm.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> It is unknown if this is a mistake or whether Clifford has succeeded Gulian over Gulian's eldest son, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Donnel_Swann\" title=\"Donnel Swann\">Donnel</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_Lords_of_Stonehelm\">Known Lords of Stonehelm</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_Stonehelm&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known Lords of Stonehelm\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Lord Swann, ruling during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys I Targaryen\">Viserys I Targaryen</a>. He was the uncle of <a href=\"/index.php/Johanna_Swann\" title=\"Johanna Swann\">Johanna Swann</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Lord Swann, ruling during the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>. He was the father of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Byron_Swann\" title=\"Byron Swann\">Byron Swann</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_.E2.80.94_a_son_for_a_son.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_.E2.80.94_a_son_for_a_son.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Gawen_Swann\" title=\"Gawen Swann\">Gawen Swann</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Manfred_Swann\" title=\"Manfred Swann\">Manfred Swann</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Gulian_Swann\" title=\"Gulian Swann\">Gulian Swann</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup> (or <a href=\"/index.php/Clifford_Swann\" title=\"Clifford Swann\">Clifford Swann</a>),<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> the current Lord of Stonehelm.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_Stonehelm&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\" style=\"-webkit-column-width:200px; -moz-column-width:200px; column-width:200px; -webkit-column-count:2; -